You're obviously thinking of someone else. You claimed in
one of your replies that I must have a lot of lag. I never
said that, nor agreed with you. I have cable modem service
and don't have 500-600 ms lag. I don't "selo-run almost
as slow as normal people run". My average ping is about
150 and my average zone time is around a minute.

If you think you can make it from Qeynos to Freeport in
20 minutes I'd love to see you do it.
